{"tid":341720,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【樂視危機】樂視手機店大規模關閉　CEO梁軍指重點是電視業務","createTime":"2017-07-31T04:38:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T04:38:55.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"49e372ed392cd4fc4d03420d54d99d90f8ef947a","tid":341720,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T04:38:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170731/large/1501469818_4000.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170731%2Flarge%2F1501469818_4000.jpg&h=1419ed64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樂視再陷入危機，內地傳媒報道指，樂視在內地的實體手機店已大規模撤店或轉型，手機維修中心亦大部份停工。<br />\n<br />\n樂視移動負責人回應指，目前在調整中，店面的第二階段戰略的轉型方案正在完善階段，目前還沒有到對外公布的時候。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，大部份樂視手機維修中心已關閉，北京11間店有10間已停止維修服務，2間更直接執笠。<br />\n<br />\n樂視網行政總裁梁軍表示，在上任兩個月以來，正調整樂視核心戰略，未來重點是電視業務，邊緣業務「該砍就砍」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57022795&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57022795%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170731&d=ioBbEwQ8bECJkkkZqHTizW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=3fcf36ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57022795%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170731&h=5506165f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57022795&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170731</a>"}]}